data.title: Grand Duchess Alexandra Georgievna (1870
data.meta_description: Photograph of Grand Duchess Alexandra Georgievna. She is standing with her head turned to the left and her left arm resting on an ornate wooden pillar beside her to the right. She is wearing Imperial court dress with a long train gathered in front of her, a sash and a tiara. She is holding a fan and a pair of gloves in her right hand.
